For questions about this project or collaboration opportunities:
- üìß Primary Contact: [chigbujoshua@yahoo.com](mailto:chigbujoshua@yahoo.com)
- üéì ALX Cohort: {COHORT_NUMBER}
- üìç Location: {LOCATION}

---

*This project is part of the ALX Software Engineering Program - Building the next generation of software engineers in Africa.*
```

## GENERATION INSTRUCTIONS

### File Naming & Location:
- **Filename**: "AUTHORS" (no extension) or "AUTHORS.md" (with markdown)
- **Location**: Repository root directory only
- **Format**: Markdown format for proper rendering

### Content Customization:
- **Replace Placeholders**: Fill in {START_DATE}, {END_DATE}, {COHORT_NUMBER}, {LOCATION}
- **Maintain Primary Author**: Keep Chigbu Joshua as primary author
- **Add Contributors**: Use template section for additional contributors when applicable
- **Project Context**: Customize acknowledgments based on specific project

### Formatting Guidelines:
- **Use Emojis**: Maintain emoji usage for visual appeal and consistency
- **Proper Links**: Ensure all email and GitHub links are functional
- **Clear Sections**: Maintain section separation with horizontal rules
- **Professional Tone**: Keep content professional yet approachable

### Dynamic Content Rules:
- **Dates**: Use actual project start/end dates
- **Cohort Info**: Include actual ALX cohort number
- **Location**: Add actual geographic location
- **Role Descriptions**: Be specific about contributions and roles

